result.name: Sushi Express -Tseung Kwan O (Conveyor Belt)

reviews.text: Not enough type of Dishes，not tasty at all

This is an awesome and rather cheap Japanese restaurant with conveyor belt for sushi and Japanese snacks. The CP value of it is high and you can pay for only a bit to get your stomach full. It is located beside a Chinese restaurant called Cafe de Carol.

Fresh sushi via a conveyor belt and at affordable prices. 

Usually a queue to get in.
Sometimes good salmon. Not always the same standard.
For the price they charged,  it was reasonable cheap dinner.

result.name: 爭鮮迴轉壽司 Sushi Express

reviews.text:
每次去到：衞生很差：膠盒污漬：很多：一点都不吃壽司的店
希望留意改善：人手不足也要留意：
客人會下次不來：就咁簡單
將軍澳 南豐廣場
食飯高峰期要排隊，由於該分店人手不足，服務及食物出品也遠不及以前了。
人手嚴重不足，迴轉線上壽司又少，食品膠蓋非常污穢。

食物算新鲜!但款式不太多1!
下午三点後清潔抹桌的後生仔似是parttime，動作懶散!另一位女員工做到不停手!
基本上坐咗半個鐘都係得嗰三幾樣壽司，結果埋單去其它餐廳食.
